      "description": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) values compared against in-vitro measurements at 5 L/min, 2500 RPM. Simulation NIH within 8% of experimental mean across three independent test runs. Inherent variability in blood sample hemolytic susceptibility assessed qualitatively by the engineering team but no structured uncertainty quantification node was linked to this result.",
