    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate NIH prediction within 8% of experimental measurements across all five operating points. RH < 1 criterion satisfied relative to predicate device. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the defined COU.",
